title: A Place Called Chiapas
description:
Movie info:

15 Fot Distro has begun distributing it's GIGANTITIOUZ archive of political documentaries online. We will still provide DVD's on anarchist book fairs and such, but mail-order via our website will cease during 2016. 

----------------------------------------------------


So - What is 15 Fot Distro?


15 Fot Distro is a project dedicated to delivering political documentaries. Our perspective is socialistic but our aim is to bring as broad a perspective of reality as we muster. 

Purpose: to inform and inspire a liberating resistance among the global working class.

Here you will find movies from around the world that deals with structural racism resistance, workplace struggle, armed struggle, animal rights, womens rights movement, antifascism as well as artfilm and portraits of alternative lifestyles. We try keep a clear classwar perspective, and therefore you will NOT find conspiracy theories concerning Illuminati, 9/11, JFK, The protocalls of the elders of Sion, or any other theoretical dead end at our place.

-----------------------------------------------------


So enjoy! But please keep in mind that we do not distribute major productions!!! We deal mainly with low budget activist movies. For this reason, you might want to seed these files for a longer time than you would after leeching Oceans Eleven 235.
